    "We can note that all FL frameworks and tools in the current state do not yet implement all the features mentioned in Sect. 2.5.",
    "The highly evolving state of FL frameworks and tools leads to unstable development of intelligent software.",
    "The most common obstacle is inconsistency among library versions, which can break up or slow down the development phase of artificial intelligence models.",
    "The appreciated use of the containerization approach may help overcome this obstacle.",
    "It is important to note that, in some cases, the PETs presented involve high computational power requirements and high memory consumption because of the underlying cryptographic and secure technologies."
